Kokujev
</taxonomicName>
♀ (MR). A) Fore wing; B) mesosoma, lateral view; C) scutellum and propodeum dorsal view; D) head, anterior view; E) head, lateral view. F–G: 
<taxonomicName authority="Szepligeti" authorityName="Szepligeti" authorityYear="1905" box="[917,1246,1811,1835]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Ophion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turcomanicus">
